<C>__{jack}
<D>__{no.}
<C>__{alan}
<D>__{so what are we gonna do, jack?}
<A>__{jack wallows for another moment in his own sadness...}
<C>__{alan }
<D>__{jack...?}
<A>__{jack snaps out of it, turning to alan and the rest of the group...}
<C>__{jack}
<D>__{ill tell you exactly what were going to do. youre going to do whatever you have to do to find out which european company hes been talking to. then im going to clean myself up, fly to aspen, and drink egg nog with bob thomas. his wife and kids will be playing in the background while i spend christmas day convincing him that the european company is the devil and global is the answer to his prayers, after all...}
<P>__{(growing wistful)}
<D>__{then im going to spend four hours skiing. alone. on christmas day. completely and utterly alone. im going to do that because that is my life, that is whats real, and there is nothing i can do to change that...}
